posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OHL/NJQP', "From your private patio or balcony at Hunters Ridge Apartments you will enjoy the beauty of the natural setting of Minnetonka's hills, woods, and wetlands.", 'Our property features underground parking, a fitness center, pool, and central laundry.', 'Hunters Ridge has controlled entries, professional on-site management and maintenance.', 'Fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Hunters Ridge home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Appliances in kitchen', 'Ceiling fan', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Elevator access', 'Trash chutes', 'Laundry facility', 'Outdoor swimming pool', 'Off street parking', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Car wash station', 'Hunters Ridge Apartments Information', 'Address:', '19000 Stratford Rd, Minnetonka MN, 55345', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=12', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Fee:', '$100 - 200 (Note: varies with pet type)', 'Pet Deposit:', '$200', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 8:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 8:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 5:00PM', 'Saturday:', '12:00PM - 3:00PM', 'Sunday:', '12:00PM - 3:00PM']
